  "2026-07-08T18:04:30.901Z",claude-code-agent,"Review evidence: addressed latest bot feedback before repush. Fixed SDK/MCP search contract leakage by keeping list-only --today/--recent out of search schemas, added help to contracts summary intents, treated programmatic updatedAfter:null as unselected, and clarified open-only today docs. Verification passed: focused tests (78 tests), CI-equivalent static sequence, and full coverage 100/100/100/100 (5463 tests)."
