  "2026-07-09T18:02:16.487Z",codex-root-20260709,"Review-loop follow-up: hardened the token-budget gate by preserving child-process environment variables, rejecting malformed manifest shape, treating bare --manifest as the default path, and making quality:static build dist before measurement. Focused release specs and quality:static passed. The shared release runCommand helper already fails nonzero child exits, so no duplicate status guard is needed."
